<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361984" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/>Nobilissimo et Celeberrimo Viro
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Joannes Polenus</rs>.</opener>
<p><lb/>Vix dici potest quam aegro animo, et
                        <lb/>quam verecundanti respondeam tibi,
                        <lb/>Nicolae Ornatissime. Vehementer enim
                        <lb/>commoreor; quod, cum olim tard<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> nimis
                        <lb/>(tametsi non mea culpa) Celeberrimo
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person"><add>P</add>atruo tuo</rs> respondere mihi contigerit,
                        <lb/>nunc tarditatis reus apud te quoque
                        <lb/>esse videar. Sed habeas, me amplius
                        <lb/>quattuor mensibus <add>a</add>fflicta valetudine
                        <lb/>laborantem, ita denique novis, et
                        <lb/>gravibus incomodis correptum fuisse,
                        <lb/>ut periculum fuerit, ne tibi respondere
                        <lb/>unquam possem. Quare necesse <add>habui</add>
                        <lb/>totum hoc tempus non modo a
  <lb/><rs type="organisation" key="org_DE-588-10021039-9">Gymnasio</rs> (ut adhuc facio) verum etiam
                        <lb/>a quolibet litt<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>rario commercio vacare.
                        <lb/>Nunc autem morbo, si non ad pacem
                        <lb/>adducto, certe ad induciar, haec tibi
  <lb/>scribo petens a te culpae liberationem<!-- Weiser -->
                        <pb facs="1361986" n="2"/>
<lb/>cum errati venia coniunctam. Atque iam
                        <lb/>venia, quemadmodum sperare iuvat, impetrata,
                        <lb/>gratias tibi ago, quod me certiorem feceris
  <lb/>de editione <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_88AUNP8T">Ephemeridum Eruditorum</rs>, quibus
                        <lb/>tamen opus mihi non est; nam vellem earum,
  <lb/>quae <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisi<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>s</rs> editae sun<add>t</add>, inchoatam seriem
                        <lb/>perficere. Quod vero adeo liberaliter
                        <lb/>paratus esses emptionem facere, et miror
                        <lb/>benignitatem tuam erga hominem tibi
                        <lb/>ferme ignotum, et gratias habeo maximas:
                        <lb/>Deus faxit, ut referre etiam aliquando ita
                        <lb/>voleam, ut facile constet, quam te colem,
                        <lb/>atque observem. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum tuum</rs> nunquam
                        <lb/>a me sine laudis praefatione nominandum
                        <lb/>meis verbis saluta. Post haec id unum addam,
                        <lb/>ut in Litterarum inscriptione caveas a
                        <lb/>quibusdam titulis, qui mihi convenire non
                        <lb/>possunt. </p><closer>Fac ut valeas, atque scias, meum
                          <lb/>animum in te, quem tu esse vis, et<!-- Weiser -->
                          <pb facs="1361987" n="3"/>
<lb/>qui esse debet, semper futurum.
                          <lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavio</rs><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> ipsis Nonis Decembribus<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> MDCCXV.</dateline>
<pb facs="1361988" n="4"/>
<address><addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
<addrLine>Monsieur <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolas Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></addrLine>
<addrLine><choice><orig>Licentie,</orig><reg>Licentié</reg></choice> en Droits</addrLine>
  <addrLine>À <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basle</rs></addrLine>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-11887733X">franca <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2775220">Inspruch</rs>.</note>
</address></closer>
